data.description: Step inside this inviting home, nestled in a serene neighborhood. You are immediately greeted by the abundance of natural lighting throughout the open concept layout, boasting a kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances and stylish cabinetry. All of the bedrooms are oversized with ample closet space for storage. The owner's ensuite is designed with comfort and convenience in mind. Take relaxation & entertaining outside to the sizable backyard. Come be part of a welcoming community with landscaped lawns and newer homes. Take a stroll down to the picnic area, playgrounds, and enjoy views of the pond. Easy access to interstates and local amenities, including shopping centers, parks, restaurants, and schools.
